@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home";
}

<section id="hero">
    <div id="heroCarousel" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel">

        <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">

            <!-- Slide 1 -->
            <div class="carousel-item active" style="background-image: url(../../Content/assets/img/LemonWash-1x-web.png);">
                <div class="carousel-container">
                    <div class="carousel-content animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
                        <h2>You know what would make house cleaning more fun?</h2>
                        <h2> A maid.</h2>
                        @*<p>Who you gonna call, Dust Busters! </p>*@
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Slide 2 -->
            <div class="carousel-item" style="background-image: url(../../Content/assets/img/LemonS.png);">
                <div class="carousel-container">
                    <div class="carousel-content animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
                        <h2>“Housework can’t kill you, but why take a chance?”</h2>
                        <h2>– Phyllis Diller</h2>
                        @*<p>You know what would make house cleaning more fun? A maid. Let us remove that stress for you.</p>>*@
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Slide 3 -->
            <div class="carousel-item" style="background-image: url(../../Content/assets/img/OrangeBubbles.png);">
                <div class="carousel-container">
                    <div class="carousel-content animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
                        <h2>Dear small line of dirt that won’t go into the dustpan,</h2>
                        <h2> I hate you with every part of my soul.</h2>
                        @*<p>Ut velit est quam dolor ad a aliquid qui aliquid. Sequi ea ut et est quaerat sequi nihil ut aliquam. Occaecati alias dolorem mollitia ut. Similique ea voluptatem. Esse doloremque accusamus repellendus deleniti vel. Minus et tempore modi architecto.</p>*@
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#heroCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon icofont-simple-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>

        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#heroCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon icofont-simple-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>

        <ol class="carousel-indicators" id="hero-carousel-indicators"></ol>

    </div>
</section><!-- End Hero -->

<main id="main">

    <!-- ======= About Us Section ======= -->
    <section id="about-us" class="about-us">
        <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">

            <div class="section-title">
                <h2><strong>About Us</strong></h2>
            </div>

            <div class="row content">
                <div class="col-lg-6" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <h2>Cleanliness, Health and Happiness. </h2>
                    <h3>Cleanliness brings joy and relieves stress. We are dedicated to also being as healthy as possible by shying away from harsh chemicals and using natural cleaners that are safe for you, your pets and us!</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 pt-4 pt-lg-0" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <p>
                        Our goal is to remove the burden of life-maintenance, helping you keep your home tidy and clean. We help you cultivate a place in which to relax and revel, an immaculate stage for entertaining friends and family. We take pride in our work and the knowledge that we help our clients live better. As the daughter and sister of two cancer survivors, I take toxicity very seriously and use only the safest and “cleanest” products to get the job done.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> Human, pet and environment friendly - enzyme based - organic cleaning agents</li>
                        <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> Flexible hours and options</li>
                        <li><i class="ri-check-double-line"></i> Professional, trustworthy staff</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="font-italic">
                        We take great care of our clients, because we start by taking great care of ourselves and our team members.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section><!-- End About Us Section -->


</main><!-- End #main -->